{"tid":1021013,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"有無解夢撚 發左個好奇怪既夢","createTime":"2019-02-14T03:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T08:32:26.000Z","uid":137088,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"32487e586d15500cc46dc4739126e225f85feec4","tid":1021013,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:35:16.000Z","msg":"一開波講我一生最終結局係被凌辭處死<br />\n之後重生幾次結局都同上面一樣<br />\n然後重生後發現唔對路 開始做出改變<br />\n搵關鍵女仔一個 同佢講我係預言者 知道自己命運 想佢幫助<br />\n之後斷片 劇情一轉<br />\n上網討論區搵到其他脫離到既人分享佢地點脫離<br />\n其中有一個人死後，有兩架火車，一架向上行，一架向下行，佢係兩架火車相遇時由向下行既火車頂跳左上向上行既火車，然後就成功了<br />\n其他人都有分享一d有creative既方法<br />\n然後又斷片<br />\n之後重生 考慮緊點做既時候就醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60121ebca5ca19db6358d81f827a57db7981d472","tid":1021013,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adb86fa27f090b1facdf1a1c362812df907dbbf6","tid":1021013,"uid":113830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:42:28.000Z","msg":"我都想俾人解 <br />\n呢排發夢開始係咁夢見自己死 /死咗  以前都未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8431ba1e08ed16423147ad88426d4b47e1cbe9e","tid":1021013,"uid":70411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:19:15.000Z","msg":"睇得太多戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604511912077dfe7498d8ccf0b79d9b2f2ac952e","tid":1021013,"uid":165431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adb86fa27f090b1facdf1a1c362812df907dbbf6","tid":1021013,"uid":113830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:42:28.000Z","msg":"我都想俾人解 <br />\n呢排發夢開始係咁夢見自己死 /死咗  以前都未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:32:26.000Z","msg":"我經常都係咁夢見自己俾人殺死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁點算？"}]}